      "acceptanceCriteria": "Configuration management, version control, and regression testing documented for CFD solver at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is under formal configuration management with documented version control and automated regression test suite covering 42 canonical cases. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 5."
    },
    {
