      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for hemolysis index QoI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed; GCI for hemolysis index is 8.2%, exceeding the 5% target for MRL 5. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 3, contributing to overall credibility gap."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
