      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same pump geometry and at operating conditions spanning the intended COU envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same device family but not the specific patient-implanted design. Operating conditions cover 4 of 5 target flow-speed combinations. Achieved level 3 is one grade below required level 4."
    },
